    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hi, nice feedback!\n\nIndeed what we would need here is maybe this: https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/issues/753#issuecomment-168701879\n- A way to update the configuration of a widget\n- A way to force a render of the interface or a render of a specific widget\n\nBoth are not so easy to do for now but ultimately this is what we would need. See https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/issues/852\n\nAs for your widget that's a very good one indeed, it would be great to have it as a community widget!\n\nWe will try to discuss those features soon, in the meantime you can comment on it and give us your feedback\n",
